Package: vortex-os-update
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: i486
Maintainer: Vortex86 A9100 Project
Description: Full OS update for Vortex86 A9100 (meta-package)
 Depends on vortex-kernel and vortex-base-system to bring
 the system up to the latest build. After installation, run:
   update-grub && reboot
Section: meta
Priority: optional
Depends: vortex-kernel (>= 1.0.0), vortex-base-system (>= 1.0.0)
Source: https://github.com/vincenzosco/Vortex-A9100-Linux-Image
